Guangzhou International Tourism Fair Opens
GUANGZHOU , February 27 ( Xinhua ) -- A gala international tourist fair opened today in Guangzhou , capital of south China 's Guangdong province .
More than 350 tourism agencies and airlines from about 20 countries and regions are represented at the fair .
During the three-day fair , seminars will be held featuring Portugal , and China 's Yunnan province , Tibet Autonomous Region , and Chaozhou and Shantou cities in Guangdong .
Guangzhou International Tourist Fair has been held annually since 1993 to promote the vibrant city 's travel industry .
